text: Speak to the children of Israel, and thou shalt say to them, If a woman having received seed shall bear a man child, She shall be unclean seven days, according to the days of separation of her flowers.

segments.text: Speak to the children of Israel, and thou shalt say to them,
If a woman having received seed shall bear a man child,
She shall be unclean seven days, according to the days of separation of her flowers.
